article.description: — Zach Austin had 17 points and eight rebounds as High Point topped Winthrop 65-56 on Monday night.
article.headline: Defense shines as High Point tops Winthrop 65-56
article.linkText: Defense shines as High Point tops Winthrop 65-56
article.story: HIGH POINT, N.C. -- — Zach Austin had 17 points and eight rebounds as High Point topped Winthrop 65-56 on Monday night. Bryant Randleman added 14 points and seven rebounds, and Jaden House had 12 points for High Point (8-11, 2/3 Big South Conference). Kelton Talford had 17 points, 10 rebounds and three blocks for the Eagles (12-7, 5-1), whose six-game win streak ended. Cory Hightower added 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
